        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Postal Facilities Security Camera Act&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This bill requires the U.S. Postal Service (USPS), subject to the availability of appropriations, to install security cameras at each USPS facility to ensure the security of its employees, customers, and property.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
